QuickyCoin,enables,businesses,to,accept,bitcoin,litecoin,and,other,crypto,currencies,as,payment,The,QuickyCoin,API,solution,is,tailored,to,a,user,s,business,enabling,bitcoin,litecoin,and,other,crypto,currencies,users,to,actually,make,payments,The,solution,immediately,enables,businesses,to,receive,litecoin,payments,and,is,scalable,to,include,other,crypto,currencies,upon,demand,An,account,is,required,with,service